name: Tiki Magazine Summer/Fall 2013 Vol. 9, No. 2
description:
This is the Summer Fall 2013 issue of Tiki Magazine.

It features articles about Tom "Big Toe" Laura, Disney's Enchanted Tiki Room, Tiki Iniki, Otto von Stroheim, George Walls, and Nick Camara himself.

Topics include tiki bars, cocktails, and the overall tiki lifestyle.

This copy is the final issue of Tiki Magazine with Nick Camara as the publisher and editor. This farewell issue is sure to be a collector's item.
